  "task": "Parse an X12 EDI 270 (eligibility inquiry) or 271 (eligibility response) transaction (5010A1). Emit normalized JSON: { format, direction, payer, provider, subscriber, dependents?, inquiry?, response? }. Direction auto-detected from ST01 (270 inquiry / 271 response). 270 carries EQ service-type-codes; 271 carries EB eligibility-benefit-information per service type.",
